snippet.title: Trine 2: Complete Story
snippet.description:
Trine 2: Complete Story integrates the Goblin Menace expansion and the unlockable  Dwarven Caverns level with the main game! 


Available on Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/35720/


Humble Store Page:
http://www.trine2.com/buy
Now DRM free for PC, Mac and Linux:


http://frozenbyte.com/games/trine-2-complete-story/
http://www.trine2.com
